===概覽模式===
Cinnamon 1.4加入了新的概覽模式，這兩個模式是“Expo”及“Scale”，可以在Cinnamon設定中自訂。

==擴充性==
Cinnamon可利用佈景主題、小工具及擴充元件進行修改。佈景主題可以自訂Cinnamon的外觀，包含但不限於選單、[[工作列|工作列]]、行事曆以及對話框。小工具可以是在工作列上的圖標或文字。預設有五個小工具放在工作列上，開發者可以自由的創建小工具。官方提供了一個如何創建小工具的教程<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cinnamon.linuxmint.com/?p=156 |title=How to make a Cinnamon applet (Force Quit applet tutorial) |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2012-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204113500/http://cinnamon.linuxmint.com/?p=156 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。擴充元件可以調整Cinnamon的功能，像是產生一個[[Dock|Dock]]或是修改視窗切換時的外觀。

開發者可以上傳他們的佈景主題、小工具以及擴充元件到Cinnamon的網頁上，讓使用者下載使用並評分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cinnamon.linuxmint.com/?p=141 |title=New sections for themes, applets and extensions: Cinnamon |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2012-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531205219/http://cinnamon.linuxmint.com/?p=141 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==採用==
Cinnamon在[[Linux_Mint|Linux Mint]] 12的套件庫中首次提供<ref name="introducing cinnamon">{{cite web |url=http://blog.linuxmint.com/?p=1910 |title=Introducing Cinnamon |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2015-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316115018/http://blog.linuxmint.com/?p=1910 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在後續的版本中與另一個桌面環境，[[MATE|MATE]]<ref name="linux mint 13 RC released">{{cite web |url=http://blog.linuxmint.com/?p=2010 |title=Linux Mint 13 "Maya" RC released! |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2015-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122221901/http://blog.linuxmint.com/?p=2010 |dead-url=no }}</ref>做為安裝時可選擇的預設桌面環境之一。在[[Linux_Mint_Debian_Edition|Linux Mint Debian Edition]]升級包4中也成為一個可選的桌面環境<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.linuxmint.com/?p=1949|title=Update Pack 4 is out!|accessdate=2013-07-16|archive-date=2013-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130821063153/http://blog.linuxmint.com/?p=1949|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

除了[[Linux_Mint|Linux Mint]]以外，Cinnamon也提供給[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]] 12.04（經由[[Personal_Package_Archive|Personal Package Archive]]）、[[Fedora|Fedora]] 18<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.redhat.com/about/news/press-archive/2013/1/fedora-18-features-updated-user-interfaces-and-desktop-environments |title=Fedora 18 Features Updated User Interfaces and Desktop Environments |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2014-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204142747/https://www.redhat.com/en/about/press-releases/fedora-18-features-updated-user-interfaces-and-desktop-environments |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[openSUSE|openSUSE]] 12.1、[[Arch_Linux|Arch Linux]]、[[Gentoo_Linux|Gentoo]]、{{link-en|Pardus linux|Pardus Linux}}、[[Manjaro_Linux|Manjaro Linux]]以及[[Sabayon_Linux|Sabayon]] 8<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.itworldcanada.com/news/sabayon-linux-8-debuts-with-a-dash-of-cinnamon/144866 |title=Sabayon Linux 8 Debuts with a Dash of Cinnamon |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924203443/https://www.itworldcanada.com/article/sabayon-linux-8-debuts-with-a-dash-of-cinnamon/45948 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。並且是{{link-en|Snowlinux|Snowlinux}}的預設桌面環境<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.snowlinux.de/625-news-snowlinux-4 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515101856/http://www.snowlinux.de/625-news-snowlinux-4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
目前，就Debian 8，同样提供Cinnamon的初始安装环境，并在官方源中提供Cinnamon安装。

==發展==
雖然Cinnamon直到2012年1月時仍在早期的發展階段，所收到的反饋普遍來說是相當不錯的。它的支持者認為相較[[GNOME_Shell|GNOME Shell]]，Cinnamon更加的有彈性、更強大，並且提供了更多進階的特性<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/blog/open-source/linux-mints-cinnamon-a-gnome-3x-shell-fork/10056 |title=Linux Mint's Cinnamon: A GNOME 3.x shell fork |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110134423/http://www.zdnet.com/blog/open-source/linux-mints-cinnamon-a-gnome-3x-shell-fork/10056 |archivedate=2012-01-10 |accessdate=2013-07-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.softpedia.com/news/Introducing-Cinnamon-The-GNOME-3-Replacement-244107.shtml |title=Introducing Cinnamon: The GNOME 3 Replacement |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2014-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415172659/http://news.softpedia.com/news/Introducing-Cinnamon-The-GNOME-3-Replacement-244107.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]並在他們對[[Linux_Mint|Linux Mint]] 17的審閱中，描述Cinnamon是「在所有平臺上，最人性化且最全方位可用的桌面。」<ref>{{cite web|author1=Scott Gilbertson|title=Mint 17 is the perfect place for Linux-ers to wait out Ubuntu uncertainty|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/06/mint-17-the-perfect-place-for-linux-ers-to-wait-out-ubuntu-uncertainty/|publisher=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|accessdate=2015-05-31|date=2014-06-24|archive-date=2015-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602201442/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/06/mint-17-the-perfect-place-for-linux-ers-to-wait-out-ubuntu-uncertainty/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==使用過時函式庫的爭論==
[[Cinnarch|Cinnarch]]，一個基於[[Arch_Linux|Arch Linux]]，使用Cinnamon做為預設桌面環境的發行版，宣布其將以GNOME取代Cinnamon，並在新的版本發行時更名為“Antergos”<ref>{{cite web|title=DistroWatch.com: Antergos|url=http://distrowatch.com/table.php?distribution=antergos|accessdate=2013-05-20|archive-date=2013-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130806092201/http://distrowatch.com/table.php?distribution=antergos|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cinnarch.com/important-notice-the-future-of-cinnarch/ |title=Important Notice: The future of Cinnarch |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425150909/http://www.cinnarch.com/important-notice-the-future-of-cinnarch/ |archivedate=2013-04-25 |accessdate=2013-07-16 }}</ref>。Clement Lefebvre在其論壇中表示讓Cinnamon相容於新版的[[GTK+|GTK+]]不是他們的首要任務<ref>{{cite web |url=https://github.com/linuxmint/Cinnamon/issues/1828#issuecomment-16286688 |title=Cinnamon needs some love |accessdate=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2019-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215125704/https://github.com/linuxmint/Cinnamon/issues/1828#issuecomment-16286688 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

